	* FvwmButtons/draw.c (RelieveButton): fixed off-by-one bug: relief
	around buttons was a bit too large

	* FvwmPager/FvwmPager.c (ParseOptions): implemented MoveThreshold as
	for main module

	* FvwmPager/x_pager.c (MoveWindow):
	(IconMoveWindow):
	fix to prevent windows in the pager to get lost off the virtual desktop
	(MoveWindow): fixed a bug that could warp a window from the last desk
	to the first desk
	(MoveWindow): move window to closest page when dragged off the virtual
	desktop (when there are more slots in the pager than pages displayed).

