	did not switch off the other type if both were used.

1998-12-10  Dominik Vogt  <dominik_vogt@hp.com>

	* FvwmButtons/parse.c:
	* FvwmButtons/output.c:
	* FvwmButtons/FvwmButtons.c: panel bugfixes by J Joshua Feng

